# API 测试集合

## 用户认证

### 1. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "测试用户",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 2. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 获取用户信息
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. 更新用户信息
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "新用户名",
  "phone": "13900139000"
}

## 失物管理

### 5. 获取失物列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items?status=pending&page=1&limit=10

### 6. 获取失物详情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items/1

### 7. 发布失物
POST http://localhost:3000/api/items
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

测试物品
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

这是一个测试物品描述
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

电子产品
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="location"

图书馆
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 8. 获取我的发布
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items/my
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. 更新失物
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "更新后的标题",
  "description": "更新后的描述",
  "category": "书籍文具",
  "location": "教室"
}

### 10. 删除失物
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. 取消招领
POST http://localhost:3000/api/items/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

## 招领管理

### 12. 申请招领
POST http://localhost:3000/api/claims/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "claimMessage": "这是我的物品，特征是..."
}

### 13. 获取招领申请列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/claims?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 14. 获取我的申请
GET http://localhost:3000/api/claims/my
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 15. 通过招领申请
POST http://localhost:3000/api/claims/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 16. 拒绝招领申请
POST http://localhost:3000/api/claims/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

## 统计数据

### 17. 获取统计数据
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics

## 通知管理

### 18. 获取通知列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 19. 标记通知为已读
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 20. 全部标记为已读
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
